name: Breathwork & Sauna
description:
Hi I'm Greg ðŸ‘‹ I want to organize a breathwork session in the sauna tonight, around 7:45pm. We'll be leveraging Othership's app guide us along the way. If you've never done breathwork, or you have but not in a sauna setting, its a truly amazing experience.

The session itself will be a bit short, it can be a bit extreme in there if you stay for too long. We'll try a beginner/intermediate class that will be 10-15 minutes long :)

If you don't know Othership, it's a really amazing sauna & icebath experience from Toronto (they're expanding). Read more about them here: https://www.othership.us/ (im not affiliated, just a big advocate of breathwork/sauna/icebaths).

<3
